*****************  TCK_0x409f0045.text  *********************
 
*****************  L0 legenda ***********************
L0 thresholds in units of ADC
ADC conversion: Calorimeter 20 Mev/ADC, Muons 40 MeV/ADC
MASK=001: apply to every crossing
MASK=010: apply only to beam1+empty crossing. L0-TCK>=29: also accept empty-empty
MASK=100: apply only to beam2+empty crossing. L0-TCK>=29: also accept empty-empty
MASK=000: mask this trigger
rate in percent, hence 100 is no prescale, 0.1 is 1/1000.

******************** TCK = 0x0045 ********************
